===Etymology===
From {{ja}} [[津波]] (つなみ, tsunami), "harbour wave"

===Pronunciation===
*tso͞o-nä'mi, /tsuːˈnɑːmi/, /<tt>tsu:nA:mi</tt>/

===Noun===
'''tsunami''' (''Plural:'' '''tsunami''' ''or'' tsunamis)

#A very large [[wave]], caused by a tremendous disturbance in the ocean, such as an [[undersea]] [[earthquake]] or volcanic eruption, that often causes colossal damage when it reaches land.

